            <title>[AMQ-2327] Consumers left hanging in the large network of brokers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-2327</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a network of brokers of a size of 4 (or more) and using conduit subscriptions, some &quot;proxy&quot; consumers can be left hanging due to circular references.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
